{"tid":407350,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"［中國新歌聲2］清泉般的歌聲—郭沁","createTime":"2017-09-20T11:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T17:39:27.000Z","uid":94075,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6fdd498d501985d6c85954a170de72447694e4","tid":407350,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"呢個囡真係不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n年紀輕輕但把聲真係清泉咁 再加埋年紀細個感覺真係好清純<br />\n雖然唔係靚女 但個外形都好文青<br />\n盲選個陣eason係第一個揀佢嘅 但佢最後都係揀左那英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/0YimVdvVh-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0YimVdvVh-g&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9cde0da9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0YimVdvVh-g</a><br />\n<br />\n個陣睇佢第一輪比賽完全比佢把聲吸引到 佢把聲係靚到會有個景象係腦海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7hg9eXfRMtg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7hg9eXfRMtg&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9e407006\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7hg9eXfRMtg</a><br />\n<br />\n唔只可以唱啲好清新嘅歌 哀怨(?!)嘅歌都拿捏得好好<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ti5fdLn-ZTg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTi5fdLn-ZTg&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2d9f75a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ti5fdLn-ZTg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xj_C5Iscqig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxj_C5Iscqig&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4dbef00b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xj_C5Iscqig</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然好鐘意Eason 但佢啲學員真係唔夠呢個女仔咁夠殺傷力<br />\n冇錯係殺傷力 佢把聲係會令到你毛管棟 會入心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a4fcf7bf77d664a64377a4d7d47824ec771452","tid":407350,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201